<div class="card shadow mx-auto">
    <h1 class="card-title"><i class="fas fa-address-card"></i> </br>BHS Job Board</h1>
    <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Post or find jobs meant for Brookline High students</h6>
    <div class="card-body">
        <a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-danger mt-auto" data-toggle="tooltip"
            title="Any BHS-affiliated Google account will be treated as a student account. Log in with a personal account to post job listings.">
            <i class="fab fa-google"></i> &nbsp; Log In With Google
        </a>
        </br>
        </br>
        <button style="margin-top: 5px;" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto" data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#instructions">Instructions</button>
    </div>

    <div id="instructions" class="collapse container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <h6>Students:</h6>
                <ol>
                    <li>Log in with your BHS Google Account</li>
                    <li>Upon logging in, you'll be able to see all current job listings</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <h6>Employers:</h6>
                <ol>
                    <li>Log in with a Google Account</li>
                    <li>Upon logging in, you'll be able to see all of your job listings.</li>
                    <li>Click the "Create New" button to create a new job listing.</li>
                    <li>Upon posting a listing, you should see it on your dashboard.</li>
                    <li>The <i class="fas fa-adjust"></i> icon will switch the status of the posting.
                        "Open" means that it is visible to students. "Closed" means that the posting is hidden.</li>
                    <li>The red button will delete the listing.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <p class="text-muted">Any BHS-affiliated Google account will be treated as a student account. Log in with a personal account to post job listings.</p>
</div>
